WEBVTT

01:38.080 --> 01:40.630
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.310 --> 01:43.630
[Episode 25]

02:35.750 --> 02:36.910
Can we go in now?

02:37.900 --> 02:38.720
Y-Yes.

02:38.740 --> 02:39.340
Of course.

02:40.190 --> 02:40.990
May I ask, sir,

02:41.079 --> 02:43.840
if you have any more extremely rare
surviving ancient texts?

02:43.840 --> 02:45.300
I do have a few more at home.

02:45.900 --> 02:46.400
Why?

02:46.630 --> 02:47.560
The Sihe Library

02:47.560 --> 02:48.840
would like to borrow
your texts for transcription

02:48.840 --> 02:50.630
and will provide books of equal value
in exchange.

02:50.630 --> 02:52.030
What do you think, sir?

02:53.430 --> 02:54.360
Maybe next time.

02:54.840 --> 02:56.310
So you agree, sir?

02:57.430 --> 02:57.960
I agree.

02:58.590 --> 02:59.450
Thank you, sir.

02:59.520 --> 03:01.720
The Sihe Library welcomes you anytime.

03:01.960 --> 03:03.100
Before you enter, sir,

03:03.100 --> 03:04.080
there are a few rules

03:04.080 --> 03:05.210
I must remind you of.

03:05.240 --> 03:05.800
I know.

03:06.630 --> 03:07.590
No noise,

03:08.000 --> 03:08.800
no copying,

03:08.960 --> 03:10.730
and no soiling or damaging the books.

03:10.730 --> 03:11.170
Right?

03:11.520 --> 03:12.150
Exactly.

03:13.030 --> 03:14.160
Please come in, sir.

03:14.190 --> 03:14.710
Thanks.

03:16.380 --> 03:25.329
[Sihe Library]

03:34.750 --> 03:36.120
Did you bring everything?

03:36.120 --> 03:36.560
Yes.

03:40.840 --> 03:41.310
Senior,

03:41.800 --> 03:43.750
didn't we tell Senior Bai the other day

03:43.750 --> 03:46.750
that we'd only be destroying
the Unparalleled Secret Magic?

03:46.750 --> 03:47.910
That was just to fool him.

03:47.910 --> 03:49.040
You believed it too?

03:50.120 --> 03:51.490
Those so-called Heavenly Talents

03:51.490 --> 03:52.340
are too rigid.

03:53.430 --> 03:55.360
They'll never amount to anything.

03:55.470 --> 03:56.310
I don't know why Master

03:56.310 --> 03:57.840
values him so much.

03:58.870 --> 03:59.430
Alright.

04:00.000 --> 04:01.460
You go handle the killing.

04:02.310 --> 04:03.240
I'll take care of

04:04.280 --> 04:05.280
the rest myself.

04:06.030 --> 04:06.690
-Yes.
-Yes.

04:21.600 --> 04:22.070
Look,

04:22.350 --> 04:23.170
Volume 124.

04:23.460 --> 04:24.860
Yes, we finally found it.

04:37.230 --> 04:38.000
How much have you memorized?

04:38.000 --> 04:38.870
Two volumes.

04:39.800 --> 04:41.000
I've only done three.

04:46.430 --> 04:47.290
Need anything?

04:48.159 --> 04:48.720
Nothing.

05:17.950 --> 05:19.190
Coated with ash

05:19.560 --> 05:20.680
between the seams...

05:20.680 --> 05:22.160
As the hammer falls again and again,

05:22.160 --> 05:23.960
the ash scatters like feathers.

05:26.070 --> 05:27.390
Am I disturbing you?

05:27.630 --> 05:28.270
How about

05:28.600 --> 05:29.800
I move somewhere else?

05:29.800 --> 05:30.270
No need.

05:30.560 --> 05:31.750
I heard you reciting and got curious.

05:31.750 --> 05:33.000
I've never read it before.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.159
You're from the Central Plains?

05:34.159 --> 05:34.680
Indeed.

05:35.390 --> 05:36.480
This is the forging chapter

05:36.480 --> 05:37.920
from Unparalleled Secret Magic,

05:37.920 --> 05:39.800
written by the Goddess Wushuang
before her ascension.

05:39.800 --> 05:41.600
It's long since been lost
in our Central Plains.

05:41.600 --> 05:43.560
It's normal that you haven't read it.

05:43.560 --> 05:44.560
I see.

05:44.950 --> 05:46.870
It's ironic when you think about it.

05:46.870 --> 05:48.120
The collection from the Central Plains,

05:48.120 --> 05:49.310
lost there

05:49.630 --> 05:50.430
yet only found again here,

05:50.430 --> 05:52.630
thousands of miles away in North Xiang.

05:53.870 --> 05:55.360
This collection is very important?

05:55.360 --> 05:56.070
Of course.

05:56.510 --> 05:57.750
It records in detail

05:57.750 --> 05:59.800
the Goddess Wushuang's forging techniques.

05:59.800 --> 06:01.920
If we can bring this collection back
to the Central Plains,

06:01.920 --> 06:02.830
our craftsmanship

06:02.830 --> 06:04.490
will surely advance further.

06:05.070 --> 06:07.040
It seems the rule of the library is

06:07.680 --> 06:08.750
that you can only read it,

06:08.750 --> 06:09.510
not copy it.

06:10.360 --> 06:11.290
Rules are fixed,

06:11.560 --> 06:12.620
but people are not.

06:13.310 --> 06:14.640
It's all stored up here.

06:16.720 --> 06:18.050
May you persevere, sir.

06:18.120 --> 06:19.240
I hope you can bring this ancient text

06:19.240 --> 06:20.190
back to the Central Plains soon

06:20.190 --> 06:21.510
and restore its former glory.

06:21.510 --> 06:21.910
I will.

06:29.430 --> 06:31.090
All fine copper and pure gold,

06:31.120 --> 06:32.600
before smelting and forging,

06:32.600 --> 06:34.120
are unbalanced in hardness and softness,

06:34.120 --> 06:35.560
and their properties are not yet settled.

06:35.560 --> 06:36.560
Only when melted

06:36.720 --> 06:38.180
and quenched in cold water

06:38.480 --> 06:40.190
do they become tempered copper

06:40.190 --> 06:41.250
and tempered gold.

06:42.630 --> 06:44.520
Every joint shall be coated

06:44.560 --> 06:46.430
with ash between the seams.

06:46.830 --> 06:48.270
As the hammer falls again and again,

06:48.270 --> 06:49.800
the ash scatters like feathers.

06:49.800 --> 06:51.630
Drawing on its refined essence
as a binding force,

06:51.630 --> 06:53.490
the piece is then melted and cast.

07:16.750 --> 07:18.120
The immortal sects are here.

07:18.120 --> 07:18.680
Run!

07:19.120 --> 07:20.430
The immortal sects are here.

07:20.430 --> 07:20.870
Run!

07:21.000 --> 07:21.530
Let's go!

07:23.000 --> 07:25.270
That gives 344.

07:25.510 --> 07:27.830
Then it comes out to 3,784.

07:28.360 --> 07:29.390
Six times six

07:38.600 --> 07:39.920
yielding...

07:49.600 --> 07:50.270
Run!

07:56.230 --> 07:56.760
Murder!

07:56.950 --> 07:57.430
Murder!

07:59.800 --> 08:00.750
Run! Run!

08:01.190 --> 08:02.190
Stop memorizing!

08:02.310 --> 08:03.390
The immortal sects are here!

08:03.390 --> 08:04.920
Grab the books and run! Run!

08:06.560 --> 08:07.510
Stop memorizing!

08:07.510 --> 08:08.910
Stop memorizing and run!

08:09.560 --> 08:10.870
The immortal sects are here!

08:10.870 --> 08:11.830
Take the books and run!

08:11.830 --> 08:13.490
Otherwise, it'll be too late!

08:13.720 --> 08:14.830
Hurry, run!

08:15.160 --> 08:16.190
Murder! Murder!

08:16.390 --> 08:18.310
Help! Help!

08:18.310 --> 08:18.830
Murder!

08:19.680 --> 08:21.000
Run! Go!

08:21.190 --> 08:21.990
Open the door!

08:22.430 --> 08:22.920
Murder!

08:23.190 --> 08:23.990
Open the door!

08:27.870 --> 08:29.450
How did the immortal sects get in?

08:29.450 --> 08:30.580
I don't know either.

08:38.030 --> 08:38.480
Hurry.

08:38.630 --> 08:39.559
Go open the door.

08:39.630 --> 08:40.200
Okay.

08:46.960 --> 08:47.750
Go open the door!

08:47.750 --> 08:48.750
Otherwise, no one can leave!

08:48.750 --> 08:49.200
What about you?

08:49.200 --> 08:50.150
Hurry! Go!

08:58.720 --> 08:59.590
Can you open the door?

08:59.590 --> 09:00.850
I need something hard.

09:01.000 --> 09:02.130
Do you have a dagger?

09:02.930 --> 09:04.330
A hairpin or wood will do.

09:07.080 --> 09:07.810
Will this do?

09:09.270 --> 09:09.720
Okay.

09:35.720 --> 09:36.630
I thought

09:36.910 --> 09:38.310
you were my father's age,

09:38.440 --> 09:39.960
so I was going to give you a quick death.

09:39.960 --> 09:41.960
I didn't expect you to be this stupid!

09:41.960 --> 09:42.870
You think they could survive

09:42.870 --> 09:43.910
after going downstairs?

09:43.910 --> 09:45.240
The main door is already locked.

09:45.240 --> 09:45.720
Today,

09:46.080 --> 09:48.140
no one is leaving this library alive!

09:49.440 --> 09:50.200
We will.

09:51.200 --> 09:52.080
We will.

09:53.080 --> 09:54.600
We will get out of here

09:54.960 --> 09:55.840
with the books

09:56.720 --> 09:57.870
and return to...

10:00.440 --> 10:01.600
the Central Plains.

10:01.870 --> 10:02.870
In your dreams!

10:29.870 --> 10:31.320
Shi Wen!

10:46.150 --> 10:46.940
Hey, buddy.

10:51.510 --> 10:52.120
Me?

10:58.080 --> 10:58.600
Sorry.

11:00.000 --> 11:00.600
It's fine.

11:00.720 --> 11:01.720
Just keep it down.

11:08.750 --> 11:09.720
As an apology,

11:10.790 --> 11:11.480
how about I tell you

11:11.480 --> 11:12.410
a little secret?

11:12.870 --> 11:13.510
No need.

11:16.230 --> 11:18.670
Those who violate the rules are to
receive 80 strokes of the cane.

11:18.670 --> 11:19.870
Have you heard of Miaojiang's

11:19.870 --> 11:20.930
bonfire festival?

11:22.320 --> 11:23.270
I'm trying to memorize here.

11:23.270 --> 11:24.360
Can you be quiet?

11:25.960 --> 11:27.240
People gather together,

11:27.240 --> 11:29.370
singing and dancing
to celebrate the festival.

11:29.370 --> 11:31.050
The blazing fire

11:31.600 --> 11:33.390
lights up half the night sky.

11:35.120 --> 11:36.980
The flames leap taller than a man,

11:38.000 --> 11:39.600
brighter than the sun,

11:40.600 --> 11:42.630
and redder than blood.

11:47.510 --> 11:48.200
In a bit,

11:48.630 --> 11:50.120
this library will be engulfed

11:50.120 --> 11:51.630
in the same flames.

11:52.720 --> 11:53.180
What...

11:54.120 --> 11:55.650
What are you talking about?

11:57.720 --> 11:58.600
I said,

11:59.790 --> 12:00.650
I will

12:01.270 --> 12:03.510
blow up this library in a bit.

12:05.030 --> 12:05.840
By then,

12:06.030 --> 12:08.160
all the books will be reduced to ashes.

12:09.670 --> 12:11.200
And your flesh and blood...

12:12.240 --> 12:13.150
will become

12:13.150 --> 12:15.030
the fuel for the fire.

12:17.360 --> 12:18.480
I'm quite curious—

12:19.670 --> 12:21.200
you demonic cultivators

12:22.390 --> 12:24.120
love reading so much.

12:24.630 --> 12:26.080
Do your books teach you

12:26.120 --> 12:27.380
how to save yourselves

12:28.870 --> 12:30.600
in desperate situations?

12:30.670 --> 12:31.240
You...

12:32.870 --> 12:34.600
You're from the immortal sect.

12:36.270 --> 12:37.390
You're sharp.

12:39.600 --> 12:41.480
I heard scholars like you can

12:41.480 --> 12:43.140
compose a poem in seven steps.

12:44.240 --> 12:45.040
Alright then.

12:45.630 --> 12:47.270
I'll take seven steps now.

12:48.360 --> 12:50.270
Let's see if you can make it out of

12:51.200 --> 12:52.750
this library

12:52.750 --> 12:53.870
in that time.

12:58.790 --> 12:59.840
-Run! Run!
-One.

13:00.390 --> 13:02.790
-Grab the ones we haven't memorized!
-Two.

13:03.270 --> 13:04.030
Three.

13:04.790 --> 13:05.670
Four.

13:06.670 --> 13:07.440
Five.

13:07.600 --> 13:08.150
Run!

13:08.240 --> 13:08.870
Six.

13:08.910 --> 13:09.860
Immortal sects are here!

13:09.860 --> 13:10.820
Seven!

13:45.000 --> 13:46.200
Something's happened at the library.

13:46.200 --> 13:46.730
Let's go!

13:46.840 --> 13:48.240
Run! Run! Run!

13:50.720 --> 13:51.510
Run!

13:51.670 --> 13:52.150
Run!

13:52.320 --> 13:53.320
The library exploded!

13:53.320 --> 13:54.000
Run!

13:55.440 --> 13:56.390
I'll go with you!

13:56.510 --> 13:57.200
You stay here

13:57.200 --> 13:58.600
and do what you should do.

14:21.120 --> 14:21.650
Make way!

14:22.320 --> 14:23.120
Out of the way!

14:23.670 --> 14:24.390
Make way!

14:31.440 --> 14:32.200
Sir,

14:33.000 --> 14:34.390
did you open the lock?

14:37.960 --> 14:39.320
What can I do to help?

14:41.390 --> 14:42.030
Books.

14:42.790 --> 14:43.790
Go find the books.

14:44.120 --> 14:45.550
The Unparalleled Secret Magic.

14:45.550 --> 14:46.910
Remember, take as many as you can.

14:46.910 --> 14:47.390
Okay!

14:47.750 --> 14:49.350
Quick, let's find the books!

14:53.630 --> 14:54.320
Volume 32.

14:54.670 --> 14:55.670
I found Volume 32!

15:00.630 --> 15:01.750
I found Volumes 7 and 15.

15:01.750 --> 15:02.240
Volume 2!

15:02.240 --> 15:02.910
I found Volume 2!

15:02.910 --> 15:04.030
Volume 27, found it!

15:04.030 --> 15:05.290
I found Volume 14 here!

15:05.510 --> 15:06.270
Volume 3 found!

15:06.270 --> 15:07.000
I found Volume 28!

15:07.000 --> 15:07.820
Volume 42!

15:11.390 --> 15:12.390
The stairs are broken.

15:12.390 --> 15:13.270
The fire's coming up.

15:13.270 --> 15:14.270
What should we do?

15:15.150 --> 15:16.550
How many volumes have you memorized?

15:16.550 --> 15:17.280
Ten volumes.

15:17.510 --> 15:18.030
Good.

15:18.550 --> 15:20.480
You've memorized more than I have.

15:20.660 --> 15:21.260
Remember,

15:21.630 --> 15:22.720
you must bring
the Unparalleled Secret Magic

15:22.720 --> 15:23.720
back to the Central Plains.

15:23.720 --> 15:24.250
You must.

15:31.390 --> 15:32.120
He opened it.

15:32.200 --> 15:32.790
Great!

15:39.550 --> 15:41.080
I can't get it open! What do we do?

15:41.080 --> 15:42.080
Look for the keys!

15:49.600 --> 15:50.240
Go!

15:50.400 --> 15:51.550
Take the books and go!

15:51.550 --> 15:52.910
Hurry! Let's go!

16:03.550 --> 16:04.880
Hurry and open the door!

16:26.080 --> 16:27.750
Go!

16:28.200 --> 16:29.130
Hurry! Let's go!

16:32.360 --> 16:32.890
Let's go.

16:34.550 --> 16:35.210
Be careful.

16:40.960 --> 16:41.630
Dajian!

16:54.910 --> 16:55.910
Follow me, hurry!

16:57.910 --> 16:58.510
Save others first!

16:58.510 --> 16:59.000
Okay.

17:17.589 --> 17:18.000
Here!

17:18.440 --> 17:18.880
Here!

17:20.790 --> 17:21.450
Be careful.

17:21.920 --> 17:22.400
Hurry.

17:37.030 --> 17:38.470
Changyuan? Changyuan?

17:39.000 --> 17:39.660
Changyuan!

17:45.720 --> 17:46.520
Changyuan...

17:50.200 --> 17:50.720
Go!

17:51.030 --> 17:51.830
It's too late!

17:55.550 --> 17:56.510
Take the books.

17:57.920 --> 17:58.640
These books

18:00.160 --> 18:03.220
were bought with the lives
of Changyuan and the others.

18:16.960 --> 18:17.490
Let's go!

18:29.200 --> 18:30.400
You evil heretics,

18:30.720 --> 18:33.520
killing you with one strike
would be too merciful.

18:33.640 --> 18:34.720
We should make you

18:34.720 --> 18:36.680
suffer every torture in the world

18:37.510 --> 18:40.110
before chopping you to pieces
and feeding you to dogs!

18:40.110 --> 18:41.790
To hell with your so-called evil heretics!

18:41.790 --> 18:42.920
To hell with your so-called
"demonic manuals"!

18:42.920 --> 18:43.830
Go to hell!

18:49.750 --> 18:51.350
Even if I die in battle today,

18:51.830 --> 18:54.360
I won't tarnish the name
of the Tianyuan Sect.

18:55.310 --> 18:56.480
My fellow disciples

18:57.400 --> 18:59.270
will definitely avenge me

18:59.920 --> 19:02.050
and slaughter every last one of you...

19:12.920 --> 19:14.380
The library has exploded.

19:14.510 --> 19:15.840
Randeng's plan failed.

19:17.030 --> 19:17.550
Guhong,

19:18.000 --> 19:19.440
take some men and guard the main routes.

19:19.440 --> 19:19.830
Yes.

19:20.440 --> 19:21.750
Everyone else, split into two groups

19:21.750 --> 19:23.160
and surround the library!

19:23.160 --> 19:23.720
No one

19:24.310 --> 19:25.160
is allowed to leave alive.

19:25.160 --> 19:25.720
Yes!

19:27.790 --> 19:29.000
Did I say you could go?

19:45.640 --> 19:46.900
How did you get in here?

19:55.000 --> 19:55.960
Those useless fools

19:55.960 --> 19:57.290
couldn't stop you, huh?

20:00.790 --> 20:02.920
You're also
one of the demonic cultivators.

20:02.920 --> 20:05.350
You were already acting strange
back in Chongling Valley.

20:05.350 --> 20:06.680
But I didn't expect you to have

20:06.680 --> 20:08.010
such a hidden identity.

20:09.030 --> 20:10.090
At a time like this,

20:10.240 --> 20:10.830
don't keep siding

20:10.830 --> 20:11.550
with them.

20:11.920 --> 20:12.900
Explain.

20:15.400 --> 20:16.460
With me here today,

20:17.200 --> 20:19.800
don't even think about
laying a finger on them.

20:45.960 --> 20:47.640
The immortal sects are closing in!

20:47.640 --> 20:48.640
We need to go, now!

20:48.680 --> 20:49.340
We can't go!

20:49.750 --> 20:51.440
So many books have already been burned!

20:51.440 --> 20:52.640
We have to transcribe the books

20:52.640 --> 20:53.110
we lost from memory,

20:53.110 --> 20:54.310
or we'll forget them!

20:55.830 --> 20:56.440
Volume 18.

20:57.390 --> 20:58.480
Who has Volume 18?

20:58.510 --> 21:00.110
I'm reciting it from memory.

21:02.310 --> 21:03.040
Volume 93...

21:03.510 --> 21:04.880
Who has Volume 93?

21:06.180 --> 21:08.510
-Open the door. Open the door!
-Volume 93!

21:09.160 --> 21:09.750
I have it!

21:15.160 --> 21:15.760
Volume 93.

21:18.440 --> 21:19.400
Volume 104.

21:20.350 --> 21:21.110
Volume 104!

21:21.110 --> 21:21.640
Here.

21:24.750 --> 21:25.550
Volume 71.

21:26.200 --> 21:26.880
71...

21:30.640 --> 21:31.440
It was burned.

21:31.680 --> 21:32.740
Only half remains.

21:33.550 --> 21:34.470
Who can recite it from memory?

21:34.470 --> 21:34.860
I can.

21:35.070 --> 21:35.930
I can recite it.

21:45.240 --> 21:46.000
I thought you were

21:46.000 --> 21:46.960
some tough guy.

21:47.270 --> 21:49.000
Turns out you're just a mortal.

21:49.510 --> 21:50.040
A mortal?

21:50.640 --> 21:52.030
Have you ascended to the Heaven Realm,

21:52.030 --> 21:53.350
or were you born of an immortal woman?

21:53.350 --> 21:55.240
You're still standing on two legs
like the rest of us.

21:55.240 --> 21:56.900
What's there to be so proud of?

21:57.030 --> 21:58.630
You overestimate yourself.

22:06.680 --> 22:07.720
Lord of Rust-Sword,

22:07.720 --> 22:08.200
hurry!

22:08.590 --> 22:09.790
Take the books and go.

22:34.120 --> 22:34.750
No wonder even you're

22:34.750 --> 22:35.720
wary of him.

22:36.510 --> 22:38.310
He really does have some skills.

22:43.920 --> 22:44.440
Lu?

22:44.880 --> 22:45.480
Go in first

22:45.550 --> 22:46.610
and guard the door.

22:47.110 --> 22:47.590
Okay.

22:54.450 --> 22:56.070
Those demonic cultivators
have their tricks.

22:56.070 --> 22:57.000
We were ambushed

22:57.240 --> 22:59.030
and had to resort to
Thunderfire Talismans,

22:59.030 --> 23:00.890
yet they still managed to escape.

23:01.470 --> 23:03.070
They're all at the teahouse.

23:03.070 --> 23:05.000
Split into four groups and attack!

23:05.550 --> 23:07.150
Destroy the demonic manuals

23:07.640 --> 23:09.510
and cut off any chance
of the demons' revival!

23:09.510 --> 23:10.070
Yes!

23:25.000 --> 23:25.510
Make way!

23:25.510 --> 23:26.040
Make way!

23:26.310 --> 23:27.510
Out of the way! Hurry!

23:33.720 --> 23:34.720
The immortal sects are on a mission.

23:34.720 --> 23:35.520
Disperse now.

23:36.070 --> 23:38.110
The Sihe Library is a sacred place
in North Xiang.

23:38.110 --> 23:38.590
Even if you...

23:38.590 --> 23:39.270
If you have any issues,

23:39.270 --> 23:41.000
take them up with your prefect.

23:41.110 --> 23:42.770
If you dare take another step,

23:43.680 --> 23:45.280
there will be consequences.

23:53.280 --> 23:54.030
Why is this taking so long?

23:54.030 --> 23:54.640
Show me your travel permit!

23:54.640 --> 23:55.300
Take it out!

23:55.720 --> 23:56.580
Travel permit.

23:57.510 --> 23:58.000
Go.

23:58.160 --> 23:59.070
Sister-in-law,

23:59.070 --> 24:00.440
they said something happened in the city.

24:00.440 --> 24:01.160
Most of the soldiers

24:01.160 --> 24:02.220
have rushed there,

24:02.310 --> 24:03.510
so they're short-handed here.

24:03.510 --> 24:04.720
But I've already paid them off.

24:04.720 --> 24:06.000
The seal for the pass

24:06.030 --> 24:07.440
should come through soon.

24:07.440 --> 24:08.880
Please be patient and wait a bit.

24:08.880 --> 24:10.340
What happened in the city?

24:10.830 --> 24:11.750
You don't know?

24:12.510 --> 24:14.160
They say cultivators from
the Central Plains immortal sects

24:14.160 --> 24:15.440
burned down the Sihe Library

24:15.440 --> 24:16.750
to hunt down demonic cultivators.

24:16.750 --> 24:18.550
Those immortal cultivators...

24:23.310 --> 24:23.830
Senior,

24:24.590 --> 24:25.390
are you going?

24:27.400 --> 24:29.240
Master is still waiting for us
at the sect.

24:29.240 --> 24:30.070
Once you go,

24:30.310 --> 24:31.240
you'll be standing

24:31.240 --> 24:32.400
against the immortal sects,

24:32.400 --> 24:34.000
making enemies of everyone.

24:34.030 --> 24:34.510
Besides, they're

24:34.510 --> 24:35.960
not some good people either.

24:35.960 --> 24:37.420
They swindled your money.

24:37.440 --> 24:38.350
You can't trust them

24:38.350 --> 24:39.110
so easily.

24:42.400 --> 24:43.000
Next in line!

24:43.000 --> 24:43.800
Move through!

24:43.920 --> 24:44.640
Sister-in-law,

24:44.640 --> 24:45.510
the stamp is done.

24:45.510 --> 24:46.240
We can go now.

24:46.270 --> 24:46.790
Next!

24:52.920 --> 24:53.750
Senior.

24:54.310 --> 24:55.110
I'm so sleepy.

24:56.030 --> 24:57.490
I want to sleep for a while.

24:57.510 --> 24:58.350
Wake me

24:58.920 --> 25:00.250
when we get there, okay?

25:01.590 --> 25:02.450
Get some sleep.

26:07.750 --> 26:09.070
Haven't seen you for a month—

26:09.070 --> 26:10.670
you've improved quite a bit.

26:11.240 --> 26:12.300
And in just a month,

26:12.510 --> 26:14.040
you've gotten much weaker.

26:15.110 --> 26:16.510
Still enough to kill you.

26:38.000 --> 26:38.400
Ink.

26:38.750 --> 26:39.550
I'm out of ink.

26:41.570 --> 26:44.770
♪ With tear-filled eyes,
we face the desolate wilds ♪

26:44.800 --> 26:47.470
♪ A thousand piles of withered bones ♪

26:47.710 --> 26:50.460
♪ The lowly, in mortal flesh,
march first ♪

26:50.480 --> 26:53.030
♪ All offered up in sacrifice ♪

26:53.950 --> 26:57.140
♪ To build the stairway to the heavens ♪

26:57.680 --> 27:00.120
♪ Forging an undying obsession ♪

27:00.790 --> 27:05.400
♪ The blade is stained with blood,
and with countless tears ♪

27:04.000 --> 27:04.510
An!

27:04.640 --> 27:05.110
Brush!

27:06.360 --> 27:09.000
♪ Sparks boil over,
and demons run rampant ♪

27:06.880 --> 27:07.510
Tang!

27:09.310 --> 27:11.310
♪ Heaven and earth
are destroyed together ♪

27:12.260 --> 27:13.840
♪ Deeply knowing that the common people ♪

27:13.900 --> 27:17.600
♪ Are an untouchable weakness ♪

27:18.570 --> 27:21.940
♪ Do not turn back
to the pain of the past ♪

27:22.250 --> 27:25.010
♪ Mindless killing must not be done ♪

27:25.320 --> 27:30.240
♪ With a clear conscience, a grand spirit
overpowers the majesty of heaven ♪

27:27.350 --> 27:27.790
Hurry!

27:28.160 --> 27:29.160
Hurry up and copy!

27:32.920 --> 27:33.590
I know you.

27:34.350 --> 27:36.240
A bounty guard from
Dongzhou Prefecture.

27:36.240 --> 27:37.480
How much did they pay you?

27:37.480 --> 27:38.680
I'll give you double.

27:38.790 --> 27:39.240
No,

27:39.880 --> 27:40.640
10 times.

27:41.310 --> 27:42.790
To kill you scum,

27:43.200 --> 27:44.240
I'd do it for free.

27:45.350 --> 27:46.680
You do have some skills.

27:47.510 --> 27:49.640
But killing you is just a matter of time.

27:49.640 --> 27:51.350
I've been running around all day,

27:51.350 --> 27:53.150
and I'd rather save some effort.

27:53.200 --> 27:54.600
Why not simply oblige me?

27:55.310 --> 27:57.040
You're that certain I'll lose?

28:06.270 --> 28:07.480
My master once told me

28:08.440 --> 28:10.270
I must travel 60,000 li in my life,

28:10.270 --> 28:12.270
raise my sword against enemies
99,000 times,

28:12.270 --> 28:13.800
and draw blood 36,000 times

28:13.960 --> 28:15.000
before this blade

28:15.200 --> 28:16.130
can shed its rust

28:16.270 --> 28:18.030
and reveal its divine brilliance.

28:18.030 --> 28:18.550
Today,

28:19.070 --> 28:20.670
I'll sharpen my blade on you.

28:21.030 --> 28:22.160
Big talk for someone

28:22.200 --> 28:23.200
so weak.

28:23.590 --> 28:24.590
I'm not just talk—

28:24.830 --> 28:25.760
I'm hard to kill!

28:38.590 --> 28:39.650
When masters duel,

28:39.680 --> 28:41.880
the outcome is decided in a brief clash.

28:42.240 --> 28:43.790
Your swordsmanship is too weak—

28:43.790 --> 28:45.830
sharp enough, but lacking steadiness.

28:45.830 --> 28:46.830
You can't beat me.

28:47.960 --> 28:48.830
Cut the crap.

28:49.160 --> 28:50.420
Are we fighting or not?

28:50.510 --> 28:52.400
Actually, I don't quite understand.

28:52.400 --> 28:53.880
You filthy demons

28:54.270 --> 28:55.270
should've just stayed curled up

28:55.270 --> 28:57.000
in the gutter where you belong.

28:57.510 --> 28:59.400
How dare you show yourselves in the open

28:59.400 --> 29:00.730
and make trouble for us?

29:20.000 --> 29:20.830
Two mortals.

29:21.920 --> 29:22.790
I want them dead

29:23.440 --> 29:24.570
within half an hour.

29:27.920 --> 29:28.650
Young Sect Master,

29:28.650 --> 29:29.510
should we move?

29:30.550 --> 29:31.110
Wait!

29:32.070 --> 29:33.070
Wait a bit longer.

29:49.550 --> 29:50.720
The tower ship can fly without wings,

29:50.720 --> 29:51.750
powered by a spiral at its stern,

29:51.750 --> 29:52.640
forged from refined iron,

29:52.640 --> 29:53.590
measuring approximately...

29:53.590 --> 29:54.650
approximately...

29:57.110 --> 29:57.660
Do you have any pills left?

29:57.660 --> 29:58.830
I need a Mind-Awakening Pill.

29:58.830 --> 29:59.490
I have some.

29:59.550 --> 30:00.000
Okay.

30:01.890 --> 30:02.720
You can't take any more.

30:02.720 --> 30:03.700
You've already had three.

30:03.700 --> 30:04.630
There's no time!

30:09.830 --> 30:10.310
An!

30:10.550 --> 30:11.000
Paper!

30:12.070 --> 30:12.640
Coming!

30:23.470 --> 30:24.800
Still not backing down?

30:37.830 --> 30:38.830
It's you.

30:55.640 --> 30:57.310
It's been almost half an hour now.

30:57.310 --> 30:58.760
I'm really curious.

30:58.880 --> 30:59.960
Why do you demons

31:00.550 --> 31:02.080
always like to wear cloaks?

31:02.830 --> 31:03.310
What?

31:04.330 --> 31:05.460
Afraid of the light?

31:13.920 --> 31:14.400
Enough.

31:15.310 --> 31:16.710
Just kill him if you want.

31:16.790 --> 31:18.520
No need to insult him like this.

31:19.310 --> 31:20.040
Look at that.

31:20.680 --> 31:21.940
An ugly thing like you,

31:22.400 --> 31:24.400
yet someone still speaks up for you.

31:25.000 --> 31:26.460
You demonic cultivators,

31:26.590 --> 31:27.920
do you become uglier

31:28.400 --> 31:29.530
and more like demons

31:30.830 --> 31:32.760
the deeper your cultivation goes?

31:41.350 --> 31:42.400
Wei Chi!

31:54.030 --> 31:54.640
Go in

31:55.400 --> 31:56.400
and kill them all.

32:08.160 --> 32:09.290
Come at me together.

32:09.750 --> 32:11.440
No matter how many of you there are today,

32:11.440 --> 32:12.750
none of them can protect you.

32:12.750 --> 32:13.270
What?

32:13.920 --> 32:15.680
Want to meddle in
other people's business again?

32:15.680 --> 32:16.310
Or

32:17.350 --> 32:18.720
have you fallen into the demonic path too?

32:18.720 --> 32:20.520
"Fallen into the demonic path?"

32:21.080 --> 32:22.200
You keep throwing those words, "demons"

32:22.200 --> 32:23.460
and "fallen," around.

32:23.590 --> 32:25.120
But what is a demon, really?

32:25.590 --> 32:27.390
Didn't your sect ever teach you?

32:27.440 --> 32:28.350
Then I'll kindly

32:28.350 --> 32:29.410
tell you once more.

32:30.030 --> 32:32.200
Those who defy the sacred authority
of the immortal sects

32:32.200 --> 32:33.790
and harm their disciples

32:34.030 --> 32:34.790
are demons.

32:36.070 --> 32:37.720
Those who steal the demonic manuals,

32:37.720 --> 32:38.850
bewitch the people,

32:39.270 --> 32:40.510
and attempt to undermine the foundations

32:40.510 --> 32:41.710
of the immortal sects

32:42.000 --> 32:42.750
are demons.

32:44.030 --> 32:45.790
Those blessed by heaven and earth

32:45.790 --> 32:47.320
with immortal perception,

32:47.720 --> 32:48.880
yet who obstinately oppose

32:48.880 --> 32:50.440
the immortal sects,

32:51.110 --> 32:52.840
are the greatest demons of all.

32:52.880 --> 32:53.510
So,

32:54.920 --> 32:56.450
you've also become a demon.

32:56.640 --> 32:57.400
And demons

32:58.350 --> 32:59.550
all deserve to die.

33:43.830 --> 33:45.030
You must guard...

33:46.550 --> 33:47.440
guard the door.

33:49.590 --> 33:50.750
Guard the door...

33:52.750 --> 33:53.350
Zhanying.

33:53.790 --> 33:54.390
Zhanying!

33:55.310 --> 33:56.160
Zhanying!

34:00.640 --> 34:01.640
Zhanying!

34:36.510 --> 34:38.440
You ought to know what it feels like

34:38.670 --> 34:40.199
to be mocked before you die.

34:59.630 --> 35:01.440
You're a disciple of the immortal sect,

35:01.440 --> 35:03.170
yet you keep breaking the rules

35:03.280 --> 35:05.140
and helping these filthy demons.

35:05.550 --> 35:06.070
What?

35:06.920 --> 35:08.650
Have you forgotten everything

35:09.190 --> 35:10.520
your master taught you?

35:11.510 --> 35:13.570
The first rule of the immortal sects:

35:14.230 --> 35:15.550
all disciples

35:16.360 --> 35:17.960
shall never use their powers

35:18.190 --> 35:19.550
to interfere in mortal affairs

35:19.550 --> 35:21.010
or disrupt worldly order.

35:21.880 --> 35:22.810
I always thought

35:23.070 --> 35:24.200
the rules were right

35:25.030 --> 35:26.960
and that I was the one who was wrong.

35:27.400 --> 35:29.000
But I don't think so anymore.

35:30.280 --> 35:31.880
What you just said was wrong.

35:32.150 --> 35:34.360
Those who stand against the immortal sects

35:34.360 --> 35:35.220
are not demons.

35:35.840 --> 35:37.440
Those who try to seize power,

35:37.480 --> 35:38.610
enslave the people,

35:38.670 --> 35:39.670
oppress the weak,

35:39.760 --> 35:42.890
and commit countless bloody crimes
are the real demons!

35:44.320 --> 35:45.110
The rules of the immortal sects

35:45.110 --> 35:46.310
are not always right.

35:47.190 --> 35:48.120
Rules are fixed,

35:49.070 --> 35:50.130
but people are not.

35:51.140 --> 35:52.740
I didn't understand before,

35:52.960 --> 35:54.490
but now I've figured it out.

35:55.510 --> 35:57.280
Right and wrong, good and evil—

35:58.150 --> 35:59.610
I have to judge for myself.

36:00.280 --> 36:01.880
Today, I question my own Dao heart,

36:01.880 --> 36:03.110
and I put this same question

36:03.110 --> 36:04.970
to you and all the immortal sects—

36:05.070 --> 36:06.800
when good and evil stand opposed,

36:06.800 --> 36:08.280
and I punish evil and uphold good,

36:08.280 --> 36:09.280
how is that wrong?

36:10.550 --> 36:11.400
You're crazy.

36:11.880 --> 36:13.690
When disciples of the immortal sects
bully the weak

36:13.690 --> 36:15.000
and oppress the powerless,

36:15.000 --> 36:15.960
I step in to help—

36:16.250 --> 36:17.510
why is that not allowed?

36:17.510 --> 36:18.380
Every person I have saved

36:18.380 --> 36:19.400
is innocent

36:19.800 --> 36:20.630
of any crime.

36:21.000 --> 36:21.920
Those I have sought to kill

36:21.920 --> 36:23.000
are steeped in blood and sin,

36:23.000 --> 36:24.400
yet they still walk free!

36:25.670 --> 36:26.660
If that is so,

36:27.480 --> 36:29.440
why have I always felt guilty

36:30.200 --> 36:31.240
and adrift?

36:38.630 --> 36:40.630
You've had a breakthrough on the spot,

36:40.630 --> 36:42.430
reaching the Golden Core Stage.

36:47.560 --> 36:50.730
♪ Pointing to the sky,
questioning the moon ♪

36:50.760 --> 36:53.980
♪ I'd rather be a wandering immortal
in the mortal world ♪

36:54.000 --> 36:57.570
♪ Right and wrong, truth and lies ♪

36:57.770 --> 37:00.780
♪ I'll face them all,
then walk this sky again ♪

37:00.810 --> 37:04.420
♪ In all the world,
I choose first the people ♪

37:04.700 --> 37:07.730
♪ How could the powerful lie drunk
in golden halls ♪

37:07.760 --> 37:11.260
♪ Even if memory shatters ♪

37:09.480 --> 37:10.000
No,

37:11.110 --> 37:12.000
it's the Nascent Soul Stage.

37:11.630 --> 37:13.060
♪ I will still break
into this mortal realm ♪

37:13.090 --> 37:16.480
♪ To demand a rightful ending ♪

37:14.320 --> 37:15.450
At this very moment,

37:15.550 --> 37:16.860
someone actually advanced.

37:16.860 --> 37:19.240
♪ I lash the darkness
with a furious strike ♪

37:20.430 --> 37:23.270
♪ Fall into the abyss,
then awaken once more ♪

37:23.000 --> 37:23.910
Nascent Soul Stage.

37:23.910 --> 37:27.020
♪ If you refuse injustice,
then open your eyes ♪

37:24.000 --> 37:24.930
You're one of us.

37:25.190 --> 37:26.590
Why are you helping them?

37:27.040 --> 37:32.080
♪ To save this world of mortal
fire and smoke ♪

37:28.190 --> 37:29.390
They all say I'm hard to kill.

37:29.390 --> 37:30.880
Come at me again if you dare.

37:30.880 --> 37:31.880
You deal with him.

38:09.550 --> 38:10.480
Why are you here?

38:12.620 --> 38:13.480
How do you feel?

38:13.920 --> 38:14.980
Never been better.

38:18.470 --> 38:19.350
I'm managing.

38:43.070 --> 38:44.320
You've taken too many pills.

38:44.320 --> 38:45.250
You need to rest.

38:45.510 --> 38:46.030
No.

38:46.360 --> 38:48.160
I haven't finished reciting it.

38:48.230 --> 38:49.190
Mind-Awakening Pills.

38:49.190 --> 38:50.610
Give me some more Mind-Awakening Pills.

38:50.610 --> 38:51.550
Stop taking them.

38:51.550 --> 38:52.670
You'll die if you take more.

38:52.670 --> 38:54.800
If the books are gone, it's truly over!

39:10.760 --> 39:11.540
Get out!

39:13.770 --> 39:14.760
The Young Sect Master ordered

39:14.760 --> 39:16.220
all the books to be burned.

39:16.230 --> 39:16.670
Yes!

39:24.960 --> 39:25.490
Get lost.

39:26.590 --> 39:27.120
Let's go.

39:32.810 --> 39:33.740
What do we do now?

39:39.960 --> 39:40.960
Almost finished.

39:41.710 --> 39:42.190
Go back.

39:42.980 --> 39:43.640
Go back now.

39:43.800 --> 39:45.510
Someone has to get the books out.

39:45.510 --> 39:46.270
I need you.

39:49.030 --> 39:49.510
Go.

39:50.110 --> 39:51.240
We can hold them off.

39:51.400 --> 39:51.880
Okay.

39:57.070 --> 39:59.230
There are 120 volumes
of Unparalleled Secret Magic.

39:59.230 --> 40:00.550
The ones we brought out of the library

40:00.550 --> 40:01.840
and the ones we've copied from memory

40:01.840 --> 40:03.370
make up exactly 64 volumes.

40:03.710 --> 40:05.110
The remaining 56 volumes

40:05.190 --> 40:06.550
are still being written from memory.

40:06.550 --> 40:07.030
Let's

40:07.360 --> 40:08.400
split into two groups.

40:08.400 --> 40:09.660
You take the 64 volumes

40:09.670 --> 40:10.590
and head west.

40:11.550 --> 40:12.680
Cross three ridges,

40:12.800 --> 40:14.510
and you can return to the Central Plains.

40:14.510 --> 40:15.640
I don't know the way.

40:19.070 --> 40:20.000
I'll go with you.

40:20.630 --> 40:21.110
Okay.

40:21.360 --> 40:21.920
Tang You!

40:22.920 --> 40:23.960
The remaining 56 volumes

40:23.960 --> 40:24.960
are in your hands!

40:26.550 --> 40:27.080
Let's go.

40:27.110 --> 40:27.630
Go.

40:31.920 --> 40:32.840
One volume short.

40:32.840 --> 40:33.570
Almost done.

40:40.030 --> 40:40.890
All 56 volumes,

40:41.400 --> 40:42.000
complete!

40:43.670 --> 40:45.130
-All done.
-That's great.

40:47.360 --> 40:47.840
Miss,

40:48.280 --> 40:50.140
can you lead us on the north route?

40:52.320 --> 40:52.920
Which way?

40:54.280 --> 40:54.960
Follow me.

40:59.000 --> 40:59.530
Let's go!

41:02.150 --> 41:02.710
Hurry!

41:07.070 --> 41:07.840
They are escaping.

41:07.840 --> 41:09.770
They have all the demonic manuals!

41:12.710 --> 41:13.990
Books! My books!

41:27.840 --> 41:28.970
Sheng, you go first.

41:29.150 --> 41:30.280
Be careful, Senior.

41:30.880 --> 41:31.410
Let's go.

41:37.190 --> 41:38.030
Why do you

41:38.960 --> 41:41.190
get tangled up with
the demonic cultivators again?

41:41.190 --> 41:42.190
Your sect ordered you to hunt down

41:42.190 --> 41:44.120
people from the Wushuang Society,

41:44.150 --> 41:45.750
and you just blindly obeyed.

41:46.710 --> 41:48.310
Have you ever read that text?

41:49.070 --> 41:50.450
Have you ever spoken

41:50.480 --> 41:51.710
with your so-called demonic cultivators?

41:51.710 --> 41:53.110
Do you know why they wanted to

41:53.110 --> 41:54.110
copy those books?

41:56.070 --> 41:57.000
Someone like you

41:57.510 --> 41:58.670
will never understand

41:58.670 --> 42:00.230
what they truly want,

42:01.110 --> 42:02.590
nor will you ever know

42:02.590 --> 42:03.320
what you've destroyed!
